Description: Monolithic Hyprland ecosystem bundle for Debian
 Builds and installs the Hyprland Wayland compositor along with its
 companion libraries and tools (hyprutils, hyprlang, hyprcursor,
 hyprgraphics, aquamarine, hyprland-protocols, hyprwayland-scanner,
 hyprwire, xdg-desktop-portal-hyprland, hypridle, hyprlock, hyprpaper,
 hyprpicker, hyprpolkitagent, hyprshutdown, hyprsunset, hyprsysteminfo,
 hyprtavern, hyprtoolkit, hyprlauncher, hyprpwcenter, hyprland-guiutils,
 hyprland-qt-support) plus rofi-wayland, swww, wallust, AGS (Aylur's
 GTK Shell), and Quickshell.
 .
 This is a personal monolithic package, not for the Debian archive. It
 builds upstream sources from git via the bundled install scripts. Build
 requires network access for git, cargo, and npm.
